==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Savingness
<hw>Sav"ing*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of
being saving; carefulness not to expend money uselessly; frugality;
parsimony.</def> <rj><au>Mrs. H. H. Jackson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tendency to promote salvation.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Savior</ent>⟦br⟧
